description.en:
Sam is a photographer, entrepreneur and surfer based in the Canary Islands. He bought his first Nikon DSLR when he was 21 and he found his passion for phography while travelling around Asia, Latin America and Europe. Often travelling solo, Sam's camera was his best travel buddy and he shot everything that captured his eye during his travels.

Sam often takes his camera out when the surf is too big. He loves to shoot candid shots of surfers, landscapes, beaches, sunsets and everything else related to the ocean.

@el_senor_sam

description.es:
Sam es un fotógrafo, emprendedor y surfista basado en las Islas Canarias. El compró su primera cámara (un Nikon DSLR) cuando tenía 21 años y encontró su pasión por la fotografía mientras viajaba por Asia, América Latina y Europa. A menudo viajando solo, la cámara era su mejor compañera de viaje y sacaba todo lo que captaba su atención durante sus viajes.

Sam suele sacar su cámara cuando las olas son demasiado grandes. Le encanta tomar fotografías espontáneas de surfistas, paisajes, playas, atardeceres y todo lo relacionado con el océano.

@el_senor_sam

description.en:
Jake started his passion for illustration whilst travelling around Mexico, He noticed someone selling stickers of his favourite place (chacahua, Mexico) and thought he should give it a go too. Within the first day he sold out all of his travel poster and sticker of Chacahua, which paid for a couple nights in a hammock and breakfast. Since then he has been drawing every place he has visited and liked.

Jake loves the canary islands, drawing every place he visits on the islands, including personal memories from each place. Now, Jake is trying to relocate permanently to Gran Canaria, where he can focus on his retro travel posters and surf illustrations.
